The paper discusses content-based image retrieval, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of low-level features such as color, texture, and shape also suggests that the paper may be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.DL) sub-categories.
